½ cup Jasmine Rice
6 ounce Broccoli
1.25 ounce Gluten-Free Tamari Sauce
1 unit Umami Stock Concentrate
¾ ounce Sriracha Sauce
10 ounce Boneless Pork Chops
1.5 ounce Canned Corn
1 ounce Edamame
2 unit Eggs
1 tsp Sugar*
Cooking Oil
Salt*
Pepper*

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.